er%202022%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20recently%20finished%20refurbishing%20the%20school%20bus%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethey%20call%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexpectation-vs-reality-van-life-trip-not-like-social-media-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVan%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fremote-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremote%20lifestyles%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20become%20increasingly%20popular%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20many%20people%20documenting%20their%20experience%20traveling%20and%20budgeting%20while%20on%20the%20road%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20making%20sure%20that%20it%20was%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20Everdeen%20said.%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%20we're%20sacrificing%20space%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20sacrifice%20our%20sanity%20or%20livelihoods%20in%20order%20to%20live%20our%20dream.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEverdeen's%20remote%20job%20allows%20her%20to%20make%20more%20and%20work%20less%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEverdeen%20calls%20herself%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-nomad-lifestyle-lessons-drawbacks-challenges-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20nomad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20term%20for%20people%20who%20travel%20freely%20while%20working%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20finds%20gigs%20on%20websites%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Da4dcb4bdca533fdc8ce70a831dbd149d625e281a492d99e850069b4d58274aa0%26postID%3D65e094cd598842733a31273a%26postSlug%3Dmillennial-makes-six-figures-freelancing-remotely-side-hustle-van-life2024-2%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.fiverr.com%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFiverr%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20flexibility%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enot%20only%20allows%20her%20to%20road%20trip%20with%20higher%20pay%20than%20her%20previous%20office%20role%2C%20but%20she%20said%20she%20only%20works%20two%20or%20three%20hours%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverdeen's%20expenses%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaving-texas-political-freedom-property-taxes-housing-costs-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20than%20they%20were%20in%20Texas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20said.%20Her%20main%20budget%20items%20are%20limited%20to%20cell%20service%2C%20food%2C%20and%20costs%20associated%20with%20parking%20and%20gas%20for%20the%20school%20bus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20she%20and%20Jared%20are%20parking%20at%20a%20campground%2C%20they%20might%20pay%20%2430%20to%20%2460%20per%20night.%20But%2C%20if%20they%20stay%20in%20a%20public%20parking%20lot%2C%20on%20public%20land%2C%20or%20with%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20it's%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20Jared%20will%20work%20at%20a%20campground%20in%20exchange%20for%20space%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20bus%20drives%20at%20about%20seven%20miles%20per%20gallon%2C%20Everdeen%20said%2C%20so%20she%20might%20spend%20%241%2C000%20on%20gas%20for%20a%20big%20drive%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she%20and%20Jared%20typically%20stay%20in%20the%20same%20place%20for%20weeks%20or%20months%20before%20moving%20on.%20She%20also%20pays%20car%20insurance%20on%20the%20bus%20and%20on%20her%202003%20Chevrolet%20that%20they%20pull%20in%20a%20trailer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20pays%20%2450%20a%20month%20for%20two%20cellphones%2C%20and%20they%20spend%20between%20%24300%20to%20%24600%20a%20month%20on%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Everdeen%20advises%20anyone%20thinking%20about%20life%20on%20the%20road%20to%20expect%20the%20unexpected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20a%20breakdown%2C%20we%20might%20spend%20%245%2C000%20fixing%20it.%20And%20not%20only%20that%2C%20you're%20also%20out%20of%20a%20place%20to%20live%20for%20a%20week%20and%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20hotel%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20embracing%20anything%20that%20comes%20your%20way%20%E2%80%94%20good%20and%20bad%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20live%20and%20to%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20this%20adventure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETraveling%20has%20given%20Everdeen%20a%20new%20outlook%20on%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEverdeen%20said%20she%20has%20learned%20a%20lot%20of%20lessons%20while%20on%20the%20road%2C%20and%20minimalism%20has%20changed%20her%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20biggest%20thing%20is%20how%20little%20we%20need%20in%20life%20to%20be%20comfortable%20and%20to%20be%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20whole%20life%20I%20was%20always%20the%20person%20who%20was%20shopping%20at%20Marshalls%20and%20T.J.%20Maxx%20and%20finding%20the%20next%20best%20thing.%20I%20couldn't%20do%20that%20anymore%20because%20I%20don't%20even%20have%20any%20wall%20space%20to%20put%20things%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20parts%20of%20traveling%20have%20been%20lonely%2C%20Everdeen%20said.%20She%20does%20not%20often%20talk%20directly%20to%20clients%20for%20her%20freelance%20work%2C%20and%20she%20doesn't%20have%20coworkers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20summer%2C%20she%20and%20Jared%20spent%20a%20few%20months%20in%20rural%20Maine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20at%20one%20point%20thinking%20to%20myself%3A%20Why%20am%20I%20so%20sad%3F%20Why%20do%20I%20feel%20depressed%3F%20And%20I%20couldn't%20figure%20it%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20somebody%20who%20loved%20me%2C%20I%20had%20a%20dog%2C%20I%20was%20taking%20care%20of%20myself.%20And%20I%20realized%20I%20was%20missing%20the%20connection%20aspect%20with%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverdeen%20said%20she%20now%20makes%20an%20effort%20to%20be%20more%20social%20when%20she%20travels%2C%20beyond%20just%20seeing%20people%20at%20grocery%20stores%20or%20while%20sightseeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20others%20have%20misconceptions%20about%20Everdeen%2C%20she%20said%2C%20and%20they%20wonder%20why%20she%20is%20living%20in%20her%20school%20bus%20by%20choice.%20But%20she%20stands%20by%20her%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20especially%20older%20people%20%E2%80%94especially%20people%20over%2070%20or%20so%20%E2%80%94%20that%20have%20really%20been%20through%20life%20and%20enjoyed%20a%20lot.%20They're%20always%20the%20ones%20to%20be%20like%2C%20'I%20am%20so%20happy%20that%20you're%20following%20your%20dreams%20and%20you're%20loving%20life%20and%20you're%20doing%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do.%26quot%3B'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20May%2C%20when%20the%20weather%20is%20warm%2C%20Everdeen%20plans%20to%20be%20in%20Montana.%20She%20might%20want%20to%20buy%20a%20house%20and%20live%20on%20a%20farm%20eventually%2C%20but%20she%20doesn't%20plan%20on%20giving%20up%20her%20life%20on%20the%20road%20any%20time%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20living%20on%20the%20road%3F%20Have%20you%20made%20a%20major%20career%20change%20to%20fit%20your%20lifestyle%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aallisonkelly%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eallisonkelly%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-makes-six-figures-freelancing-remotely-side-hustle-van-life2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709459461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e0b6996080194819fb3d18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-makes-six-figures-freelancing-remotely-side-hustle-van-life2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alice%20Everdeen%20works%20multiple%20gigs%20to%20support%20her%20digital%20nomad%20life%2C%20but%20she%20only%20works%20a%20few%20hours%20each%20day%20and%20brings%20in%20six