B%20Matt%20Martian%20Williams%3B%20Andrea%20Ellen%20Reed%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMaria%20Maki%2C%2079%2C%20experienced%20her%20%26quot%3Bdeepest%20sense%20of%20loneliness%26quot%3B%20when%20she%20moved%20to%20Buffalo%2C%20Minnesota%2C%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20attempted%20to%20mitigate%20her%20feelings%20of%20isolation%20by%20reading%20and%20doing%20various%20projects%20at%20home%2C%20but%20Maki%20told%20me%20that%20between%20not%20having%20close%20contact%20with%20family%20members%20and%20living%20alone%20in%20a%20new%20city%2C%20she%20reached%20a%20point%20where%20%26quot%3Benough%20is%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20in%20teal%20sitting%20by%20table%20and%20looking%20away%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e201266080194819fb9fd3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaria%20Maki%20at%20the%20Buffalo%20Community%20Center%20in%20Buffalo%2C%20Minnesota.%3Cp%3EAndrea%20Ellen%20Reed%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20outlook%20shifted%20in%20March%20of%20last%20year%20when%20she%20saw%20a%20woman%20post%20on%20Nextdoor%2C%20an%20app%20meant%20to%20connect%20people%20in%20the%20same%20neighborhood%2C%20saying%20she%20was%20also%20new%20to%20the%20area%20and%20lonely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImmediately%2C%2030%20women%20responded%2C%20and%20I%20was%20one%20of%20the%20women%20who%20quickly%20responded%20and%20said%2C%20'Let's%20meet%20for%20coffee%20over%20at%20our%20local%20coffee%20shop%20and%20set%20a%20date%2C'%26quot%3B%20Maki%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20four%20of%20us%20showed%20up%2C%20and%20then%20the%20four%20of%20us%20talked%2C%20and%20we%20were%20glad%20to%20meet%20each%20other.%20We%20posted%20it%20back%20on%20Nextdoor%2C%20and%20the%20next%20week%2C%20we%20had%2015%20people%2C%20and%20that%20was%20too%20crowded%20for%20the%20coffee%20shop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surge%20in%20interest%20led%20Maki%20to%20contact%20the%20local%20community%20center%20to%20request%20a%20room%20where%20the%20women%20could%20gather.%20Demand%20grew%20so%20strong%20that%20they%20split%20into%20smaller%20groups%20that%20were%20more%20conducive%20to%20talking%20and%20forming%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20of%20older%20women%20sitting%20in%20a%20circle%20laughing%20and%20talking.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e1e4dfce7f1785b2e54283%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20group%20of%20women%20gathered%20at%20the%20Buffalo%20Community%20Center%3Cp%3EAndrea%20Ellen%20Reed%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20anxious%20to%20find%20a%20group%20of%20friends%20in%20Buffalo%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20I%20jumped%20at%20the%20invitation%20to%20meet%20at%20the%20coffee%20shop%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20going%20ever%20since%2C%26quot%3B%20Maki%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20been%20a%20lifesaver%2C%20not%20just%20for%20me%2C%20but%20for%20some%20of%20the%20other%20people%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaki%20isn't%20exaggerating%3A%20Finding%20a%20cure%20for%20loneliness%20could%20indeed%20save%20lives.%20In%20May%2C%20US%20Surgeon%20General%20Vivek%20Murthy%20declared%20loneliness%20an%20epidemic%2C%20and%20he%20initiated%20a%20call%20for%20action%20to%20mitigate%20its%20harmful%20impacts%3A%20increased%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease%2C%20stroke%2C%20and%20dementia%20in%20older%20adults.%20Loneliness%20also%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20early%20death%20by%20more%20than%2060%25%2C%20per%20Murthy's%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20loneliness%20among%20older%20adults%20has%20been%20an%20issue%20for%20years%2C%20the%20pandemic%20exacerbated%20it%20across%20all%20age%20groups.%20Gen%20Zers%20have%20told%20Business%20Insider%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-loneliness-spends-money-to-make-friends-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolutions%20to%20their%20loneliness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20joining%20fitness%20groups%20or%20taking%20art%20or%20cooking%20classes.%20But%20older%20people%20often%20don't%20have%20those%20options%20and%20tend%20to%20be%20more%20socially%20isolated%20as%20their%20families%20move%20away%20and%20long-term%20friendships%20dwindle.%20They%20need%20to%20find%20more%20accessible%20solutions%20to%20stimulate%20social%20interaction.%20Some%20experts%20told%20me%20that%20cities%20could%20help%20counter%20loneliness%20with%20policies%20that%20bolster%20senior%20centers%20and%20ensure%20accessibility%20to%20vital%20resources%20and%20that%20governments%20should%20invest%20more%20in%20mitigating%20loneliness%20for%20older%20adults.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20some%20of%20those%20adults%20are%20taking%20matters%20into%20their%20own%20hands%20to%20ensure%20life%20doesn't%20pass%20them%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20happier%2C%26quot%3B%20Maki%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20I%20have%20a%20group%20of%20people%20I%20can%20talk%20to%20or%20call%2C%20and%20I've%20done%20some%20of%20the%20outside%20activities%2C%20which%20has%20been%20fun.%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20it%20all%20week%2C%20and%20without%20that%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20I'd%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20women%20sitting%20by%20a%20table%20and%20smiling.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e20157ce7f1785b2e55c2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaria%20Maki%20with%20her%20community%20center%20friends.%3Cp%3EAndrea%20Ellen%20Reed%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEven%20a%20small%20connection%20can%20be%20a%20'lifesaver'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Lamy%2C%2075%2C%20retired%20in%202021.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20when%20he%20lost%20interactions%20with%20his%20coworkers%2C%20he%20struggled%20to%20find%20new%20ways%20to%20connect%20with%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20ready%20to%20slide%20into%20obscurity%2C%20he%20contacted%20his%20local%20senior%20center%20in%20Seattle%20to%20facilitate%20a%20group%20for%20older%20adults%20to%20gather%20and%20talk%2C%20free%20of%20charge.%20Lamy%20described%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20lifesaver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20had%20our%20first%20meeting%2C%20I%20asked%20them%2C%20'How%20many%20of%20you%20have%20people%20you%20can%20talk%20to%3F'%20And%20only%20half%20the%20people%20raised%20their%20hand%2C%26quot%3B%20Lamy%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20said%2C%20'Do%20you%20mean%20to%20tell%20me%20that%20four%20of%20you%20don't%20have%20any%20person%20you%20can%20talk%20to%20in%20your%20life%20about%20anything%3F'%20And%20they%20said%2C%20'Yes%2C%20that's%20why%20we're%20here.'%20And%20it%20just%20broke%20my%20heart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20with%20curly%20white%20hair%20and%20a%20black%20sweater%20looking%20at%20the%20camera%20by%20a%20window%20with%20plants%20around%20him.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e1f507ce7f1785b2e55085%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoe%20Lamy%20at%20his%20local%20senior%20center%20in%20Seattle.%3Cp%3EJovelle%20Tamayo%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDianne%20Stone%2C%20the%20associate%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Council%20on%20Aging's%20National%20Institute%20of%20Senior%20Centers%2C%20told%20me%20that%20while%20older%20adults%20have%20had%20high%20loneliness%20rates%20for%20years%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20anything%20good%26quot%3B%20came%20out%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bwinder%20recognition%20of%20just%20how%20significant%20a%20problem%20loneliness%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20emphasized%20the%20difference%20between%20being%20lonely%20and%20being%20socially%20isolated%20%E2%80%94%20while%20%26quot%3Bisolation%20is%20the%20circumstance%20and%20loneliness%20is%20the%20feeling%20around%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bolder%20adults%20do%20tend%20to%20become%20more%20socially%20isolated%2C%20so%20they're%20at%20higher%20risk%20of%20loneliness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20largely%20why%20Lamy%20felt%20compelled%20to%20organize%20an%20easy%20way%20for%20older%20adults%20in%20the%20community%20to%20meet%20and%20talk%20to%20one%20another.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20I've%20taken%20on%20the%20role%20of%20illuminator%20in%20helping%20people%20see%20themselves%20and%20become%20comfortable%20in%20themselves%20so%20that%20they%20can%20develop%20those%20relationships%20that%20are%20so%20meaningful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20after%20my%20first%20conversation%20with%20Lamy%20in%20January%2C%20he%20followed%20up%20to%20tell%20me%20he'd%20received%20a%20flood%20of%20interest%20from%20people%20across%20the%20country%20seeking%20to%20become%20facilitators%20for%20groups%20at%20their%20own%20senior%20centers.%20He's%20now%20working%20with%20organizations%20in%20other%20states%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.friendship-facilitator.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20help%20connect%20people%20with%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20focusing%20more%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20frequent%20social%20interaction%20could%20give%20older%20adults%20a%20simple%20and%20free%20option%20to%20prevent%20loneliness%20as%20they%20age%20while%20proving%20that%20people%20don't%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20work%20and%20making%20money%20to%20find%20fulfillment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20little%20moments%20that%20are%20actually%20more%20important%20in%20our%20joy%20than%20making%2020%20bucks%2C%26quot%3B%20Lamy%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20that%20money's%20not%20important.%20It%20just%20doesn't%20fill%20you%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20of%204%20older%20adults%20setting%20up%20group%20word%20games%20on%20the%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e1f4b890413ab8e1d83a3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoe%20Lamy%20and%20his%20community%20group%20setting%20up%20the%20group%20activity%20on%20the%20table.%3Cp%3EJovelle%20Tamayo%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Opportunity's%20not%20going%20to%20knock%20on%20my%20door'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Lamy%20found%20connections%20at%20his%20local%20senior%20center%2C%20it%20hasn't%20been%20so%20easy%20for%20Jan%2C%20who%20moved%20to%20Las%20Vegas%20from%20New%20York%20two%20years%20ago%20after%20separating%20from%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJan%2C%2060%20%E2%80%94%20who%20requested%20her%20last%20name%20be%20withheld%20for%20privacy%20%E2%80%94%20said%20that%20while%20she%20now%20lives%20close%20to%20her%20mother%2C%20that's%20just%20about%20the%20only%20meaningful%20social%20interaction%20she's%20had%20with%20anyone%20since%20her%20move.%20Her%20dealings%20with%20neighbors%20consist%20solely%20of%20small%20talk%20and%20smiles%20exchanged%20in%20passing%3B%20no%20one%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20to%20grab%20a%20coffee%20or%20see%20a%20movie%2C%20and%20she's%20terrified%20that'll%20never%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20people%20have%20family%20or%20friends%20or%20a%20significant%20other.%20I%20don't%20have%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Jan%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20am%20alone.%20And%20my%20worries%20are%2C%20what%20happens%20when%20I%20can't%20walk%20up%20and%20down%20the%20stairs%20here%20at%20my%20apartment%3F%20What%20happens%20when%20I'm%20sick%20and%20I%20need%20help%3F%20I%20don't%20have%20anybody.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20Jan%20whether%20she'd%20attempted%20to%20find%20solutions%20to%20her%20loneliness%2C%20like%20reaching%20out%20to%20local%20organizations%20or%20finding%20groups%20in%20which%20she%20might%20find%20people%20with%20shared%20interests.%20She%20said%20she%20had%20contacted%20numerous%20organizations%20in%20her%20area%2C%20including%20some%20Jewish%20groups.%20Still%2C%20the%20process%20was%20burdensome%20for%20her%20and%20required%20frequent%20follow-ups%2C%20as%20she%20said%20the%20people%20she%20was%20in%20contact%20with%20were%20busy%20and%20difficult%20to%20get%20ahold%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20lead%20such%20a%20solitary%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Jan%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20alone%20every%20day%2024%2F7.%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20company.%20There's%20never%20anybody%20in%20my%20apartment%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20means%20to%20go%20anywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpportunity's%20not%20going%20to%20knock%20on%20my%20door%20and%20say%2C%20'We're%20here%20to%20give%20you%20an%20opportunity.'%20Of%20course%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20have%20that%20desire%20or%20that%20'umph'%20anymore%20to%20go%20out%20and%20look%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20January%202023%20survey%20of%20US%20adults%20ages%2050%20to%2080%20by%20the%20National%20Poll%20on%20Healthy%20Aging%2C%20one%20in%20three%20respondents%20reported%20infrequent%20contact%20with%20people%20outside%20their%20homes%2C%20with%2037%25%20saying%20they'd%20felt%20a%20lack%20of%20companionship%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20time%20in%20the%20past%20year.%20Preeti%20Malani%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20medicine%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%20who%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20National%20Poll%20on%20Healthy%20Aging's%20research%20team%2C%20told%20me%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20you're%20lonely%2C%20maybe%20there's%20not%20much%20interest%20in%20taking%20care%20of%20yourself.%26quot%3B%20And%20that%20can%20have%20health%20impacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPurpose%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20health%2C%20and%20when%20you%20look%20at%20people%20who've%20suffered%20a%20lot%20of%20losses%2C%20and%20you're%20like%2C%20'I%20don't%20know%20how%20you%20are%20able%20to%20get%20out%20of%20bed%20every%20day%2C'%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20it's%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20Malani%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20idea%20that%20what%20I'm%20doing%20is%20really%20important%20to%20others.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarey%20Schmidt%2C%2066%2C%20was%20able%20to%20find%20a%20purpose%20that%20has%20helped%20him%20avoid%20loneliness.%20After%20moving%20from%20a%20Chicago%20suburb%20to%20Sedona%2C%20Arizona%2C%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20said%20the%20only%20person%20he%20knew%20in%20the%20area%20was%20his%20real-estate%20agent%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20knew%20that%20had%20to%20change.%20A%20self-described%20introvert%2C%20Schmidt%20said%20it%20wasn't%20easy%20for%20him%20to%20step%20out%20of%20his%20comfort%20zone%20and%20take%20a%20stab%20at%20meeting%20new%20people.%20But%20he%20figured%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20lose%2C%20so%20he%20posted%20on%20Nextdoor%20to%20see%20whether%20anyone%20in%20the%20area%20wanted%20to%20meet%20him%20for%20coffee.%20Turns%20out%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20on%20chair%20with%20two%20dogs%20sitting%20next%20to%20him.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e0b5c46080194819fb3c9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGarey%20Schmidt%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Sedona%2C%20Arizona%3Cp%3EMatt%20Martian%20Williams%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20now%20have%20a%20core%20group%20of%20about%2017%20people%20that%20are%20still%20together%202%20%C2%BD%20years%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20a%20really%20nice%20group%20of%20people%2C%20and%20we%20help%20each%20other%20out%20with%20different%20things%2C%20like%20what%20doctors%20we're%20seeing%20and%20who%20we%20go%20to%20for%20repairs%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20needed%20a%20shoulder%20surgery%2C%20but%20I%20was%20taking%20a%20plane%20out%20of%20Flagstaff%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20couples%20said%2C%20'We'll%20take%20you%20there.'%20So%20it's%20a%20very%20helpful%20group%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalani%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Byour%20immunology%20changes%20when%20you%20experience%20joy%20and%20togetherness%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Schmidt%20said%20he%20had%20experienced%20that%20shift.%20Since%20the%20group%20grew%20too%20large%20for%20a%20coffee%2C%20it%20now%20meets%20at%20someone's%20house%20every%20Wednesday.%20Schmidt%20acknowledged%20it%20wasn't%20easy%20to%20put%20himself%20out%20there%2C%20but%20he%20said%20that%20after%20learning%20more%20about%20the%20loneliness%20epidemic%20and%20the%20effects%20it%20could%20have%20on%20older%20adults%2C%20he%20was%20grateful%20that%20he%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20may%20not%20know%20of%20all%20the%20different%20ways%20you%20can%20get%20out%20there%2C%20and%20it%20just%20breaks%20my%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20really%20lonely%20people%20in%20the%20end%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20one%20of%20those%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20of%20older%20adults%20sitting%20outside%20laughing%20and%20talking%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e0b69190413ab8e1d7e0b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGarey%20Schimdt's%20group%20of%20friends%20in%20Sedona.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Martian%20Williams%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20cost%20of%20loneliness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20does%20loneliness%20have%20a%20significant%20mental%20and%20physical%20toll%20%E2%80%94%20it%20can%20be%20increasingly%20costly%20the%20longer%20it%20goes%20unresolved.%20Sen.%20Chris%20Murphy%2C%20a%20Democratic%20lawmaker%20in%20Connecticut%20who%20in%20December%20introduced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.murphy.senate.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fmurphy-casey-introduce-bill-to-fight-social-isolation-and-loneliness-among-older-americans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20bill%20meant%20to%20combat%20loneliness%20among%20older%20Americans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20me%20that%20addressing%20loneliness%20%26quot%3Bcan%20save%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20in%20our%20healthcare%20system%20because%20slowly%2C%20loneliness%20tends%20to%20increase%20your%20likelihood%20of%20heart%20disease%2C%20stroke%2C%20and%20dementia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20living%20longer%20and%20being%20active%20longer%2C%26quot%3B%20Murphy%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20with%20family%20starting%20to%20scatter%2C%20and%20more%20kids%20because%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20because%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20are%20having%20to%20move%20further%20away%2C%20older%20adults%20end%20up%20getting%20isolated.%20What%20we%20know%20is%20that%20isolation%20and%20loneliness%20among%20older%20people%20tend%20to%20lead%20to%20pretty%20serious%20health%20complications%20very%20quickly.%20So%20there%20is%20a%20real%20reason%20for%20us%20to%20try%20to%20help%20older%20people%20find%20connection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERick%20Grossman%2C%2070%2C%20found%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenior-villages-loneliness-making-friends-in-retirement-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20solution%20to%20avoid%20the%20costs%20of%20loneliness%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20while%20also%20helping%20him%20navigate%20the%20other%20expenses%20that%20come%20naturally%20with%20aging.%20Grossman%20told%20me%20it%20was%20hard%20for%20him%20to%20maintain%20relationships%20while%20moving%20around%20his%20whole%20life%20and%20having%20a%20range%20of%20jobs%2C%20including%20a%20teacher%2C%20a%20salesman%2C%20and%20a%20toy%20store%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20moved%20to%20Seattle%20about%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20was%20living%20alone%20and%20struggling%20to%20find%20lasting%20connections%20%E2%80%94%20until%20he%20learned%20about%20senior%20villages%2C%20a%20network%20of%20nonprofits%20across%20the%20US%20that%20connect%20older%20adults%20in%20their%20geographical%20region%20through%20resources%20and%20activities.%20Members%20pay%20dues%20that%20help%20fund%20the%20villages%20on%20a%20sliding%20scale%20depending%20on%20involvement%2C%20and%20the%20villages%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20be%20virtual%20but%20connect%20people%20in%20the%20same%20geographic%20region%20%E2%80%94%20allow%20them%20to%20live%20where%20they%20choose%20while%20still%20having%20access%20to%20virtual%20and%20in-person%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20in%20gray%20shirt%20looking%20to%20his%20left%20in%20front%20of%20a%20blue%20building%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e1f6a46080194819fb95dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERick%20Grossman%20in%20front%20of%20his%20apartment%20building%20in%20Seattle.%3Cp%3EJovelle%20Tamayo%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20lessons%20in%20just%20preparing%20all%20of%20those%20horrible%20things%20that%20you%20have%20to%20do%20as%20seniors%2C%20handling%20wills%20and%20doing%20medical%20power%20of%20attorney%20and%20all%20of%20those%20other%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Grossman%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20avoiding%20those%20things%20for%20so%20long%2C%20and%20I%20think%20many%20people%20have.%20Nobody%20likes%20to%20do%20that.%20But%20if%20you%20do%20that%20with%20a%20group%20of%20other%20people%20that%20you%20know%2C%20it's%20a%20lot%20easier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20may%20not%20be%20feasible%20for%20everyone%20to%20pay%20dues%20to%20find%20relationships%2C%20Grossman%20says%20the%20cost%20is%20worth%20it%20to%20him%20because%20he%20no%20longer%20has%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20mental%20toll%20of%20loneliness%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20fear%20that%20if%20something%20were%20to%20happen%20to%20him%2C%20no%20one%20would%20ever%20find%20out.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20be%20more%20concerned%20about%20other%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20just%20abandon%20people%20when%20they%20age.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20and%20lawmakers%20have%20put%20forth%20solutions%20meant%20to%20prevent%20Americans%20from%20becoming%20isolated%20and%20lonely%20as%20they%20age.%20Stone%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20access%20to%20local%20senior%20centers%20to%20help%20older%20adults%20connect%20with%20their%20communities%2C%20along%20with%20ensuring%20states%20implement%20policies%20and%20funding%20that%20support%20loneliness%20mitigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20make%20this%20work%3F%20Prioritizing%20things%20like%20transportation%20infrastructure%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20it's%20all%20truly%20accessible%20so%20that%20people%20can%20get%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20Stone%20said.%20%26quot%3BSupporting%20those%20community-based%20organizations%20is%20incredibly%20important.%20Along%20with%20senior%20centers%2C%20we're%20also%20talking%20about%20libraries.%20We're%20talking%20about%20parks%20and%20recreation.%20These%20are%20all%20community-funded%20and%20government-funded%20initiatives%2C%20so%20prioritizing%20them%2C%20I%20think%2C%20is%20incredibly%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeff%20Keilson%2C%20a%20senior%20vice%20president%20at%20Advocates%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organization%20that%20works%20to%20help%20people%20facing%20developmental%20and%20mental%20health%20challenges%20%E2%80%94%20has%20succeeded%20in%20receiving%20government%20funding%20to%20address%20loneliness%20in%20Massachusetts.%20In%20January%20of%20last%20year%2C%20the%20state's%20attorney%20general%20(now%20governor)%2C%20Maura%20Healey%2C%20awarded%20%242.9%20million%20to%2011%20organizations%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20Advocates'%20initiative%2C%20the%20Friendship%20Project.%20The%20project%20connects%20residents%20experiencing%20social%20isolation%20with%20volunteers%20who%20visit%20their%20homes%20and%20accompany%20them%20on%20various%20tasks%2C%20like%20going%20out%20to%20get%20groceries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20us%20are%20able%20to%20make%20friendships%20on%20our%20own.%20A%20lot%20of%20us%20are%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Keilson%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BWe%20sometimes%20use%20various%20ways%20to%20help.%20And%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20it's%20a%20particularly%20more%20acute%20challenge.%20But%20we've%20seen%20how%20just%20connecting%20people%20with%20volunteers%2C%20the%20ripple%20effects%20on%20that%2C%20and%20how%20great%20it%20is.%20So%20if%20this%20is%20an%20area%20with%20additional%20focus%20and%20additional%20resources%2C%20we%20could%20see%20the%20results%20in%20fairly%20dramatic%20ways.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20looking%20out%20the%20window%20from%20an%20apartment%20building%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e1f63bce7f1785b2e551b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERick%20Grossman%20looking%20out%20the%20window%20from%20the%20apartment%20building.%3Cp%3EJovelle%20Tamayo%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMurphy%20said%20he's%20working%20to%20get%20more%20of%20his%20colleagues%20in%20Congress%20on%20board%20and%20encourage%20them%20to%20start%20to%20pay%20more%20attention%20to%20the%20issue%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bit's%20just%20harder%20to%20ignore%20as%20a%20crisis.%26quot%3B%20Grossman%20isn't%20ignoring%20the%20crisis%20because%20he's%20lived%20through%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he's%20discovered%20how%20social%20connections%20can%20truly%20be%20lifesaving%20if%20the%20proper%20infrastructure%20is%20in%20place%20to%20make%20them%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20I%20think%20our%20society%20just%20wants%20to%20protect%20themselves%20against%20certain%20things.%20They%20hide%20from%20aging%20by%20not%20being%20with%20seniors%2C%20or%20they%20worry%20about%20themselves%20becoming%20poor%2C%20so%20they%20avoid%20contact%20with%20the%20poor%2C%26quot%3B%20Grossman%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20social%20beings%2C%20and%20we%20just%20need%20those%20connections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomers-retirement-loneliness-making-friends-lifesaver-solutions-epidemic-happiness-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709458861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e216dc90413ab8e1d85dd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomers-retirement-loneliness-making-friends-lifesaver-solutions-epidemic-happiness-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Baby%20boomers%20have%20been%20hit%20especially%20hard%20by%20the%20loneliness%20epidemic.%20Some%20are%20finding%20ways%20to%20ensure%20they%20don't%20spend%20retirement%20in%20isolation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomers-retirement-loneliness-making-friends-lifesaver-solutions-epidemic-happiness-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Varun-Natasha%20make%20stylish%20entry%20at%20Ambani%20bash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709458731000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108179384%2Cimgsize-23666.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollyw