e.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20entering%20the%20field%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20pay%20less%20attention%20to%20the%20General%20Schedule%20levels%2C%20which%20is%20a%20hierarchal%20pay%20scale%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20you%20read%20the%20announcement%20to%20understand%20the%20qualifications%20and%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20OPM%20spokesperson%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20federal%20jobs%20don't%20have%20an%20education%20requirement%20but%20require%20some%20kind%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20position%20you're%20applying%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20jobs%20require%20an%20online%20assessment%20as%20part%20of%20the%20application%20process%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20study%20or%20take%20a%20class%20for%20these%20assessments%2C%20an%20OPM%20spokesperson%20said.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you're%20applying%20to%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usajobs.gov%2Fjob%2F777606500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etranslator%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20take%20a%20language%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUSAjobs.com%20also%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usajobs.gov%2Fnotification%2Fevents%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elist%20of%20career%20fairs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20hiring%20events%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%20virtual.%20These%20are%20also%20worth%20checking%20out%20and%20attending%20so%20that%20you%20can%20better%20understand%20the%20application%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhere%20to%20look%20for%20state%20and%20county%20jobs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EState%20or%20county%20jobs%20are%20listed%20on%20state%20or%20local%20government%20websites.%20You%20can%20find%20these%20opportunities%20by%20searching%20the%20name%20of%20the%20state%20and%20%26quot%3Bjobs%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20search%20engine%20to%20take%20you%20straight%20to%20the%20page%20with%20listings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20then%20be%20able%20to%20find%20a%20list%20of%20open%20vacancies%20in%20varying%20fields.%20Usually%2C%20these%20sites%20will