sinessinsider.com%2Fgut-health-dietitian-microbiome-foods-meals-30-plants-a-week-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20eating%2030%20plants%20a%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20simple%20with%20BI.%20She%20doesn't%20like%20to%20plan%20her%20meals%20in%20advance%2C%20but%20a%20weekly%20grocery%20shop%20allows%20her%20to%20reach%20her%20nutritional%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EVegetables%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMorse%20always%20includes%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20fresh%20vegetables%20in%20her%20weekly%20food%20shop%20and%20often%20uses%20them%20as%20the%20base%20of%20her%20meals.%20Vegetables%20are%20a%20good%20source%20of%20fiber%2C%20which%20is%20good%20for%20gut%20health%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20well%20as%20trying%20to%20mix%20it%20up%20each%20week%20to%20diversify%20her%20diet%2C%20she%20decides%20which%20produce%20to%20go%20for%20based%20on%20what's%20on%20offer%2C%20what's%20in%20season%2C%20and%20what%20can%20be%20locally%20sourced%20for%20environmental%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20a%20typical%20week%2C%20she'll%20buy%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EKale%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBell%20peppers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ETomatoes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EZucchini%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBroccoli%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EPotatoes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EMushrooms%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ECarrots%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ECelery%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EOnions%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EGarlic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EPickled%20beetroot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ESalad%20leaves%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bag%20of%20premade%20stirfry%20vegetables%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3EFruits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMorse%20also%20buys%20a%20range%20of%20fruits%20each%20week.%20She%20typically%20puts%20fruit%20in%20her%20breakfast%2C%20which%20tends%20to%20be%20overnight%20oats%20or%20eats%20it%20as%20a%20snack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%