t%20A.K.%20Ramanujan%20had%20told%20him%20and%20Kambar.%20Everything%20about%20that%20evening%20in%20my%20memory%20is%20surreal.%20He%20for%20some%20reason%20was%20standing%20while%20we%2C%20Shankar%20and%20I%2C%20sat%20on%20the%20steps%20with%20our%20folks%20from%20%5BMalgudi%20Days%5D.%20%E2%80%A6%20Girish%E2%80%99s%20voice%20pierced%20the%20night%20sky%20and%20prevailed%20over%20the%20sound%20of%20wild%20nocturnal%20life%20in%20Agumbe%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20discussions%20of%20rituals%2C%20reptiles%2C%20the%20paranormal%20and%20much%20else%20also%20followed.%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20experienced%20a%20night%20sky%20like%20that%20ever%20after%2C%20layered%20with%20a%20timeless%20story%20in%20a%20voice%20and%20erudition%20as%20rich%20as%20his.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnad%20had%20heard%20two%20folktales%20from%20Ramanujan.%20The%20first%20was%20the%20tale%20of%20%3Cem%3EA%20Story%20and%20a%20Song%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20suppressed%20deep%20inside%20a%20woman%2C%20fighting%20to%20enter%20the%20world%20and%20be%20freed.%20The%20second%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Serpent%20Lover%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20was%20about%20a%20woman%20with%20an%20uncaring%20husband%2C%20a%20man%20constantly%20preoccupied%20by%20his%20mistress.%20She%20receives%20a%20magic%20love%20potion%2C%20but%20ends%20up%20feeding%20it%20to%20a%20snake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fci3.googleusercontent.com%2Fmeips%2FADKq_NZ2t969lrkDVdK-CiLv-hoSZ_owosUofAhQxRyxwTebW2LoGlF72Ai8BtUaMeBt5SBqBHnexItdC1KC2JjCxJpRYh1p_svK-sRXbevRA9KrcF70TomYWTsVu-sMIyKkVLaOs_bRKDv0gecPH7ZkodAou1Ck32gQ7Thz-JVpdsEkB1eD32zLe4PCk1wKm8AkRq_lX1ATPK6BK0pKbbieRh5XJjY8q8Xk9ksNVooVub7e1PBYR0wfSc9g2JrYbFManxYlfHtlAl-Bc9R41UtdkQAIkexO3K0vq3VBAvxx-p_uNbybnQzhpw2s7A%3Ds0-d-e1-ft%23https%3A%2F%2Fsubstackcdn.com%2Fimage%2Ffetch%2Fw_1456%2Cc_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cq_auto%3Agood%2Cfl_progressive%3Asteep%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%252Fpublic%252Fimages%252Fd8b247d8-a7