l%20Monk%2C%20Centre%20and%20Left%3A%20Nirupama%20Nityanandan%20and%20Stan%20Egi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn%E2%80%99t%20hard%20to%20watch%20or%20read%20%3Cem%3ENagamandala%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20come%20away%20with%20a%20view%20of%20it%20as%20a%20simple%20Indian%20folktale%3A%20a%20magical%20story%20with%20an%20otherworldly%2C%20shape-shifting%20cobra%2C%20an%20archetypal%20evil%20husband%2C%20a%20wise%20old%20woman%2C%20and%20a%20beautiful%20heroine%20who%20triumphs%20and%20lives%20happily%20ever%20after.%20But%20the%20play%20has%20inspired%20a%20rich%20variety%20of%20critical%20interpretations%2C%20drawing%20on%20the%20many%20ways%20it%20has%20been%20performed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20way%20it%20centres%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20emotional%20needs%20and%20sexual%20desire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaya%20Pandit%20remarked%20that%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20tender%2C%20playful%2C%20and%20sensuous%20nights%20with%20Naga%2C%20and%20her%20%E2%80%9Cdrab%20and%20dull%20existence%20when%20the%20real%20husband%20comes%20home%20to%20eat%20at%20day%E2%80%A6%20symbolise%20the%20contradiction%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20life%20in%20general.%E2%80%9D%20For%20Aparna%20Dharwadkar%2C%20Karnad%E2%80%99s%20play%20created%20a%20world%20in%20which%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20desire%20is%20not%20just%20articulated%2C%20but%20is%20a%20powerful%20force%20that%20can%20control%20fates%2C%20and%20is%20in%20itself%20desired%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprize%20for%20which%20men%20willingly%20or%20unwillingly%20sacrifice%20themselves.%E2%80%9D%20Thus%2C%20%E2%80%9CRani%20moves%20from%20a%20position%20of%20total%20abjection%20to%20one%20of%20unqualified%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F0ba7b622-1a14-42fc-94df-9e298548d0ba%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiMTczZmEifQ.PBNXJqnQKBHgeEYkqjXtgIIV9VR-pvgw3K2feHvkCXU%26source%3Dgmail-imap%26ust%3D1709721865000000%26us