0%99%20%E2%80%98No%2C%20no%2C%E2%80%99%20Das%20corrected%20him.%20%E2%80%98She%20drowns%20her%20individuality%20in%20her%20domesticity%20and%20becomes%20a%20nothing.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20as%20the%20fourth%20edition%20of%20the%20weekly%20newsletter%2C%20The%20World%20of%20Girish%20Karnad.%20Subscribe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fworldofgirishkarnad.substack.com%2F%3Fr%3Dhzn2u%26utm_campaign%3Dsubscribe-page-share-screen%26utm_medium%3Dweb%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709456914000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03132158%2Funnamed-17.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fthe-extraordinary-story-of-girish-karnads-nagamandala%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20isn%E2%80%99t%20hard%20to%20watch%20or%20read%20Nagamandala%20and%20come%20away%20with%20a%20view%20of%20it%20as%20a%20simple%20Indian%20folktale%3A%20a%20magical%20story%20with%20an%20otherworldly%2C%20shape-shifting%20cobra%2C%20an%20archetypal%20evil%20husband%2C%20a%20wise%20old%20woman%2C%20and%20a%20beautiful%20heroine%20who%20triumphs%20and%20lives%20happily%20ever%20after.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fthe-extraordinary-story-of-girish-karnads-nagamandala%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shehbaz%20Sharif%20Returns%20As%20Pakistan's%20Prime%20Minister%20For%202nd%20Term%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShehbaz%20Sharif%2C%20returning%20as%20Pakistan's%20prime%20minister%20for%20a%20second%20time%20on%20Sunday%20when%20his%20brother%20declined%20a%20fourth%20term%2C%20has%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20holding%20together%20a%20disparate%20coalition%20for%2016%20months%20after%20rival%20Imran%20Khan%20was%20ousted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%2C%2072%2C%20won%20a%20parliamentary%20vote%20for%20premier%2C%20resuming%20the%20role%20he%20had%20held%20until%20August%20when%20parliament%20was%20dissolved%20ahead%20of%20last%20month's%20elections.%20Pakistan%20has%20had%20a%20caretaker%20government%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20named%20by%20his%20party%20and%20coalition%20allies%20to%20head%20the%20South%20Asian%20nation%2C%20despite%20his%20elder%20brother%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20winning%20a%20seat%20in%20the%20assembly%20and%20being%20favourite%20to%20be%20sworn%20in%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENawaz%20Sharif%20did%20not%20want%20to%20run%20a%20minority%20coalition%20government%2C%20having%20had%20clear%20majorities%20in%20his%20three%20previous%20stints%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20his%20daughter%20Maryam%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers'%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20party%20won%20only%2080%20of%20the%20264%20seats%20up%20for%20contest%20in%20the%20elections%20but%20was%20supported%20by%20other%20parties%20for%20a%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20holding%20the%20coalition%20together%20after%20Khan%20was%20voted%20out%20in%202022%2C%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20helped%20Pakistan%20secure%20a%20last-gasp%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20bailout%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20regained%20the%20top%20job%20as%20the%20PML-N%20buried%20differences%20with%20the%20powerful%20military%20in%20the%20face%20of%20their%20common%20rival%2C%20Khan%2C%20who%20was%20at%20odds%20with%20top%20generals%20over%20policy%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20was%20in%20self-imposed%20exile%20in%20London%20and%20disqualified%20from%20holding%20public%20office.%20He%20returned%20to%20Pakistan%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20his%20stint%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20younger%20Sharif%20was%20known%20more%20as%20an%20administrator%20than%20a%20politician%2C%20having%20served%20as%20chief%20minister%20thrice%20in%20the%20country's%20largest%20province%2C%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20he%20quickly%20took%20on%20the%20role%20of%20peacemaker%20between%20coalition%20parties%20often%20at%20odds%20with%20one%20another%20over%20key%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShehbaz%20Sharif's%20biggest%20achievement%20in%20his%20short%20tenure%20was%20clinching%20the%20IMF%20bailout%20with%20Pakistan%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20a%20debt%20default.%20The%20deal%20was%20signed%20after%20Sharif%20personally%20called%20on%20IMF%20chief%20Kristalina%20Georgieva%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20under%20his%20government%2C%20inflation%20touched%20a%20high%20of%2038%25%20with%20record%20depreciation%20of%20the%20rupee%20currency%20-%20mainly%20due%20to%20structural%20reforms%20necessitated%20by%20the%20IMF%20programme%20to%20stabilise%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20blames%20the%20economic%20meltdown%20on%20Khan's%20government%2C%20which%20he%20says%20broke%20an%20agreement%20with%20IMF%20just%20before%20he%20was%20ousted.%20Sharif%20said%20his%20government%20had%20to%20introduce%20a%20slew%20of%20reforms%20and%20scrap%20subsidies%2C%20causing%20inflation%20to%20surge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKEY%20CHALLENGES%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20continues%20to%20be%20enmeshed%20in%20economic%20crisis%20with%20inflation%20remaining%20high%2C%20hovering%20around%2030%25%2C%20and%20economic%20growth%20slowing%20to%20around%202%25.%20February%20inflation%20dipped%20slightly%20to%2023.1%25%20from%20a%20year%20earlier%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20a%20high%20base%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%20will%20need%20to%20emulate%20his%20feat%20of%20securing%20a%20short-term%20IMF%20bailout%20with%20the%20current%20programme%20expiring%20next%20month%20and%20a%20new%20extended%20deal%20needed%20to%20keep%20Pakistan%20on%20a%20narrow%20path%20to%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20main%20role%20will%20be%20to%20maintain%20ties%20with%20the%20military%2C%20which%20has%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20dominated%20Pakistan%20since%20independence.%20Unlike%20his%20elder%20brother%2C%20who%20has%20had%20a%20rocky%20relationship%20with%20the%20military%20in%20all%20his%20three%20terms%2C%20the%20younger%20Sharif%20is%20considered%20more%20acceptable%20and%20compliant%20by%20the%20generals%2C%20analysts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20several%20years%2C%20the%20military%20has%20denied%20it%20interferes%20in%20politics.%20But%20it%20has%20in%20the%20past%20directly%20intervened%20to%20topple%20civilian%20governments%20three%20times%2C%20and%20no%20prime%20minister%20has%20finished%20a%20full%20five-year%20term%20since%20independence%20in%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrivatising%20some%20lumbering%20state%20giants%2C%20including%20the%20national%20airline%2C%20and%20securing%20foreign%20investment%20will%20also%20be%20key%20to%20ease%20the%20economic%20crisis.%20The%20Sharis%20have%20close%20ties%20with%20rulers%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20Qatar%2C%20which%20could%20help%20in%20securing%20investments%20in%20several%20projects%20Pakistan%20has%20lately%20showcased%20for%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20defence%20and%20key%20foreign%20policy%20decisions%20are%20largely%20influenced%20by%20the%20military%2C%20Sharif%20will%20have%20to%20juggle%20relations%20with%20the%20U.S.%20and%20China%2C%20both%20major%20allies.%20He%20is%20also%20faced%20with%20dealing%20with%20fraying%20ties%20with%20three%20of%20Pakistan's%20four%20neighbours%2C%20India%2C%20Iran%20and%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'WORKAHOLIC'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%20was%20born%20in%20the%20eastern%20city%20of%20Lahore%20in%20a%20wealthy%20Kashmiri-origin%20family%20that%20was%20in%20the%20steel%20business.%20He%20started%20his%20political%20career%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Punjab%20in%201997%20with%20a%20signature%20%26quot%3Bcan-do%26quot%3B%20administrative%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20cabinet%20members%20and%20bureaucrats%20who%20have%20worked%20closely%20with%20him%20call%20him%20a%20workaholic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20younger%20Sharif%20planned%20and%20executed%20a%20number%20of%20ambitious%20infrastructure%20mega-projects%2C%20including%20Pakistan's%20first%20modern%20mass%20transport%20system%20in%20Lahore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20national%20political%20upheaval%20when%20his%20brother%20was%20ousted%20from%20the%20premiership%20by%20a%20military%20coup%20in%201999%20and%20he%20went%20into%20exile%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%20entered%20the%20national%20political%20scene%20when%20he%20became%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20PML-N%20after%20the%20elder%20Sharif%20was%20found%20guilty%20in%202017%20on%20charges%20of%20concealing%20assets%20related%20to%20the%20Panama%20Papers%20revelations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarried%20twice%2C%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20has%20two%20sons%20and%20two%20daughters%20from%20his%20first%20marriage%20but%20none%20from%20the%20second.%20One%20of%20the%20sons%20is%20in%20politics%20but%20the%20others%20are%20not%20in%20public%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20second%20wife%20is%20Tehmina%20Durrani%2C%20the%20well-known%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BMy%20Feudal%20Lord%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20autobiography%20about%20an%20abusive%20married%20life%20with%20an%20earlier%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709456700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-04%2F8f58ecr_shehbaz-sharif-pakistan-reuters-650_625x300_18_April_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fshehbaz-sharif-elected-as-pakistans-prime-minister-for-2nd-term-5167752%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shehbaz%20Sharif%2C%20returning%20as%20Pakistan's%20prime%20minister%20for%20a%20second%20time%20on%20Sunday%20when%20his%20brother%20declined%20a%20fourth