-e-Taiba%20(LeT)%20operative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20said%20investigators%20have%20gathered%20certain%20information%20from%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20footage%20from%20the%20city's%20public%20transport%20buses%20was%20also%20being%20analysed%20as%20part%20of%20the%20probe%20to%20nab%20the%20culprit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeveral%20teams%20have%20been%20formed%20to%20investigate.%20In-depth%20investigation%20is%20going%20on%20with%20seriousness%2C%20some%20traces%20have%20been%20found.%20Some%20information%20has%20been%20gathered%20from%20CCTV%20footage...there%20is%20information%20that%20he%20(suspect)%20had%20come%20by%20bus.%20So%2C%2026%20buses%20have%20been%20verified%20at%20Bangalore%20Metropolitan%20Transport%20Corporation%20(BMTC)%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Parameshwara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Btheory%20of%20elimination%26quot%3B%2C%20more%20buses%20are%20being%20verified%20for%20footage%2C%20as%20BMTC%20buses%20have%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20moment%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20say%20whether%20any%20organisation%20or%20an%20individual%20was%20involved%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20said.%20There%20were%20certain%20theories%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20cafe%20last%20night%2C%20expressing%20suspicion%20that%20someone%20might%20have%20done%20it%20out%20of%20%26quot%3Bheartburn%26quot%3B%2C%20unable%20to%20digest%20the%20cafe's%20success%20and%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20look%20into%20all%20angles.%20Whichever%20angle%20it%20might%20be%2C%20we%20will%20verify%20them%20and%20catch%20the%20culprits%20behind%20the%20blast%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20sources%2C%20images%20of%20the%20suspect's%20movement%20have%20been%20captured%20by%20the%20CCTV%20cameras%20at%20Rameshwaram%20cafe%20and%20those%20nearby.%20The%20CCTV%20footage%20shows%20the%20suspect%20with%20a%20bag%2C%20wearing%20a%20cap%20and