nd%20he%20is%20currently%20under%20observation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Francis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20front%20half%20of%20the%20bike%20was%20severely%20damaged%20due%20to%20the%20accident.%20The%20left-handed%20batter%20suffered%20bruises%20on%20his%20right%20knee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20for%20his%20big-hitting%20abilities%2C%20Minz%20is%20a%20left-handed%20batter%20and%20a%20devoted%20fan%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20cricketing%20journey%20is%20guided%20by%20the%20experienced%20coach%20Chanchal%20Bhattacharya%2C%20who%20also%20mentored%20the%20former%20Indian%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20hailing%20from%20the%20Gumla%20district%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20Minz%20came%20into%20the%20spotlight%20when%20noticed%20by%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20who%20facilitated%20his%20training%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%20residing%20in%20the%20Namkum%20area%20of%20Ranchi%2C%20Jharkhand's%20capital%2C%20Minz%2C%20despite%20not%20yet%20representing%20the%20state%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%2C%20has%20been%20part%20of%20Jharkhand's%20U19%20and%20U25%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20father%2C%20a%20retired%20army%20personnel%2C%20now%20works%20as%20a%20guard%20at%20the%20Birsa%20Munda%20Airport%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20and%20Minz%20shares%20his%20home%20with%20his%20two%20sisters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20Minz%20underwent%20trials%20with%20various%20franchises%2C%20including%20Lucknow%20Supergiants%2C%20Delhi%20Capitals%2C%20and%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders.%20Despite%20going%20unsold%20in%20the%20IPL%202023%20auction%2C%20Minz%20secured%20a%20significant%20payday%20in%20this%20edition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20might%20make%20his%20IPL%20debut%20in%20the%20upcoming%20season.%20The%20competition%20for%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20pl