20find%20interesting.%20As%20time%20goes%20by%2C%20they%20start%20researching%20on%20the%20techniques%2C%20companies%2C%20artists%2C%20styles%2C%20printers%20and%20their%20values.%20When%20the%20collection%20becomes%20large%2C%20one%20often%20tends%20to%20forget%20what%20one%20has%20acquired.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20Thakral%20also%20has%20an%20enormous%20collection%20of%205%2C000%2C%20one-of-a-kind%2C%20original%20popular%20visual%20arts%20in%20the%20form%20of%20old%20calendars%2C%20posters%2C%20oleographs%20and%20prints.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20not%20to%20waste%20money%20on%20duplicates%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20catalogue%20them%2C%20so%20that%20one%20has%20a%20ready%20reckoner%20of%20what%20one%20has%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Thakral.%20The%20collection%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20catalogued%20and%20maintained%20under%20the%20Tarun%20Thakral%20Archival%20collection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03121634%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-12.15.43-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03121634%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-12.15.43-PM.png%20864w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03121634%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-12.15.43-PM-300x156.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699887%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22448%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201994%2C%20Thakral%20had%20begun%20collecting%20vintage%20and%20classic%20automobiles%20and%20related%20transport%20objects.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20collection%20grew%20to%20an%20extent%20that%20he%20was%20finding%20it%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20it.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20he%20founded%20the%20Heritage%20Transportation%20Trust%20to%20promote%20the%20preservation%20of%20modes%20of%20transportation%20that%20have%20been%20used%20in%20India.%20In%202009%2C%20he%20approached%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%20to%20open%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20comprehensive%20Heritage%20Transport%20Museum%20and%20received%20a%20grant%20of%20Rs%206%20crores%20to%20set%20it%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocated%20near%20Gurugram%2C%20it%20opened%20its%20doors%20to%20visitors%20in%20December%202013%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2013%20crores%20with%20funding%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20private%20and%20corporate%20donations%20as%20well%20as%20personal%20funding.%20After%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20the%20museum%20has%20welcomed%20over%202%20million%20visitors%2C%20received%20several%20national%20and%20international%20awards%2C%20and%20been%20rated%20as%20one%20of%20the%20best%20museums%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03121740%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-12.15.56-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22940%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03121740%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-12.15.56-PM.png%20940w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03121740%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-12.15.56-PM-300x152.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699889%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22476%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20future%2C%20Thakral%20plans%20to%20create%20an%20online%20museum%20of%20visual%20arts%2C%20so%20that%20scholars%20can%20use%20it%20for%20research%2C%20education%20and%20pure%20fascination.%20He%20also%20plans%20to%20make%20sets%20of%20his%20collection%2C%20so%20that%20they%20can%20travel%20as%20temporary%20displays%20to%20various%20art%20museums%20in%20India%20and%20overseas.%20%E2%80%9CWho%20knows%2C%20it%20may%20trigger%20a%20desire%20for%20others%20to%20start%20a%20collection%20of%20their%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concludes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Journey%20Through%20Time%3A%20%2B1%20Day%2C%20%2B1%20Story%E2%80%99%20will%20continue%20at%20the%20Atrium%20Lobby%20(Longitude)%2C%20Le%20Meridien%2C%20New%20Delhi%20till%20March%2015th%2C%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENeha%20Kirpal%20is%20a%20free-lance%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709449921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03120357%2FCopy-of-Copy-of-Lead-image-size-5.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fwhat-vintage-posters-tell-us-about-india-of-yesteryear%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20posters%20from%201920s-60s%20are%20on%20display%20at%20the%20Le%20Meridien%2C%20New%20Delhi%20till%20March%2015th%2C%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fwhat-vintage-posters-tell-us-about-india-of-yesteryear%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cop%2C%20Naxalite%20killed%20in%20encounter%20in%20Chhattsigarh's%20Kanker%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709449645000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108178213%2Cimgsize-477111.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcop-naxalite-killed-in-encounter-in-chhattsigarhs-kanker%2Farticleshow%2F108176548.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Constable%20Ramesh%20Kurethi%20of%20Bastar%20Fighters%20was%20killed%20with%20a%20Naxalite%20in%20an%20encounter%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Kanker%20district.%20An%20AK-47%20rifle%20was%20recovered%20from%20Hidur%20village%2C%20within%20Chhotebethiya%20police%20station's%20jurisdiction.%20The%20gunfight%20occurred%20in%20a%20forest%20during%20an%20anti-Naxal%20operation%20based%20on%20precise%20information.%20The%20official%20further%20informed%20that%20the%20search%20operations%20were%20underway.%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcop-naxalite-killed-in-encounter-in-chhattsigarhs-kanker%2Farticleshow%2F108176548.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20Dispute%20With%20Investors%2C%20Byju%20Raveendran%20Says%20Can't%20Pay%20Salaries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20ongoing%20financial%20crisis%20in%20Byju's%2C%20company%20CEO%20Byju%20Raveendran%20on%20Saturday%20said%20that%20the%20edtech%20firm%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20pay%20the%20salaries%20of%20its%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran%20informed%20the%20news%20to%20his%20staffers%20in%20an%20email%2C%20wherein%20he%20also%20lashed%20out%20at%20a%20group%20of%20investors%20for%20moving%20a%20resolution%20to%20lock%20the%20company's%20funds%20in%20a%20separate%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20by%20Mr%20Raveendran%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6.I%20regret%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20we%20will%20still%20be%20unable%20to%20process%20your%20salaries%E2%80%A6..Unfortunately%2C%20a%20select%20few%20(4%20out%20of%20our%20150%2B%20investors)%20have%20stooped%20to%20a%20heartless%20level%2C%20ensuring%20that%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20utilise%20the%20funds%20raised%20to%20pay%20your%20hard-earned%20salaries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReasoning%20the%20scenario%2C%20Mr%20Raveendran%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20their%20behest%2C%20the%20amount%20raised%20through%20the%20rights%20issue%20is%20currently%20locked%20in%20a%20separate%20account.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20revealed%20that%20the%20funds%20had%20been%20locked%20away%2C%20even%20after%20%E2%80%9Csome%20of%20these%20investors%20have%20already%20reaped%20substantial%20profits.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20agonizing%20reality%20that%20some%20of%20these%20investors%20have%20already%20reaped%20substantial%20profits%20%E2%80%93%20in%20fact%2C%20one%20of%20them%20has%20made%20a%20staggering%20eight%20times%20their%20initial%20investment%20in%20Byju's.%20And%20yet%2C%20their%20actions%20convey%20a%20callous%20disregard%20for%20our%20lives%20and%20livelihoods.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20our%20best%20efforts%2C%20we%20are%20left%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20confront%20the%20heart-wrenching%20reality%20that%20we%20are%20temporarily%20unable%20to%20provide%20you%20with%20the%20financial%20support%20you%20deserve.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran%20claimed%20that%20the%20company%20is%20trying%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20pay%20the%20salaries%20by%20March%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20striving%20to%20ensure%20that%20your%20salaries%20are%20paid%20by%20the%2010th%20of%20March.%20We%20shall%20make%20these%20payments%20the%20moment%20we%20are%20permitted%20to%20do%20so%20as%20per%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran%20informed%20that%20last%20month%2C%20the%20company%20faced%20challenges%20in%20crediting%20salaries%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20capital%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20now%20the%20firm%20is%20%E2%80%9Cexperiencing%20a%20delay%20despite%20having%20funds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20all%2C%20we%20now%20have%20funds%20to%20meet%20our%20short-term%20needs%20and%20clear%20our%20liabilities.%20However%2C%20I%20regret%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20we%20will%20still%20be%20unable%20to%20process%20your%20salaries.%20Last%20month%2C%20we%20faced%20challenges%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20capital%2C%20and%20now%20we%20are%20experiencing%20a%20delay%20despite%20having%20funds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20concluded%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CCountless%20hours%20have%20been%20spent%20exploring%20every%20possible%20avenue%2C%20engaging%20our%20legal%20teams%2C%20and%20advocating%20for%20your%20rights.%20However%2C%20despite%20our%20best%20efforts%2C%20we%20are%20left%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20confront%20the%20heart-wrenching%20reality%20that%20we%20are%20temporarily%20unable%20to%20provide%20you%20with%20the%20financial%20support%20you%20deserve.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20primary%20stakeholders%20of%20Byju's%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20oust%20Mr.%20Raveendran%20from%20his%20position%20as%20CEO%20and%20remove%20him%20from%20the%20board%20of%20the%20company%20he%20founded%20in%202015.%20Byju's%20has%20experienced%20a%20significant%20downturn%2C%20with%20a%20notable%20decline%20of%20around%2090%25%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709449620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F2l14saa_byjus_625x300_03_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fbyju-s-unable-to-pay-salaries-as-some-investors-blocked-funds-ceo-byju-raveendran-5167129%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amidst%20the%20ongoing%20financial%20crisis%20in%20Byju's%2C%20company%20CEO%20Byju%20Raveendran%20on%20Saturday%20said%20that%20the%20edtech%20firm%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20pay%20the%20salaries%20of%20its%20employees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fbyju-s-unable-to-pay-salaries-as-some-investors-blocked-funds-ceo-byju-raveendran-5167129%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2