0to%20disturb%20the%20investigation.%20I%20will%20post%20it%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20shared%20on%20her%20Instagram%20stories.%20In%20a%20video%20uploaded%20to%20her%20stories%20the%20woman's%20face%20can%20be%20seen%20swollen%20and%20bruised%20following%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20face%20looks%20like%20this%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20what%20hurts%20me%20the%20most.%20I%20thought%20we%20were%20going%20to%20die.%20Thank%20God%20we%20are%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManhunt%20On%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20arrested%20three%20men%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20the%20crime.%20A%20manhunt%20is%20now%20underway%20to%20apprehend%20the%20remaining%20accused.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20has%20been%20constituted%20to%20ensure%20a%20thorough%20and%20swift%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDumka%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SP)%2C%20Pitambar%20Singh%20Kherwar%2C%20said%20yesterday%20that%20the%20local%20police%20patrolling%20team%20discovered%20the%20distressed%20couple%20late%20on%20Friday%20night.%20Speaking%20in%20Spanish%2C%20the%20victims%20struggled%20to%20communicate%20with%20the%20cops.%20The%20police%2C%20sensing%20the%20urgency%2C%20immediately%20transported%20them%20to%20a%20local%20hospital%2C%20where%20the%20horror%20of%20what%20they%20had%20endured%20was%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survivor%20and%20her%20husband%20are%20currently%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20Phulo%20Jhano%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Dumka.%20Although%20both%20are%20out%20of%20immediate%20danger%2C%20doctors%20are%20monitoring%20the%20couple%20for%20possible%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20are%20out%20of%20danger%20and%20are%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20the%20hospital.%20The%20man%20has%20sustained%20minor%20injuries.%20The%20medical%20examination%20of%20the%20victim%20will%20be%20done%20by%20a%20medical%20board%20comprising%20three%20gynaecologists%2C%20a%20radiologist%2C%20an%20orthopaedic%20and%20a%20dentist%2C%20headed%20by%20superintendent%20of%20the%20medical%20college%2C%20Dr%20Anupuran%20Purti%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20doctor%20at%20the%20hospital%20said%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECondemnation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20(NCW)%20visited%20Dumka%20and%20criticised%20the%20police's%20alleged%20incapability%20in%20promptly%20apprehending%20all%20the%20accused.%20NCW%20Chairperson%2C%20Rekha%20Sharma%2C%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20victim%2C%20promising%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20authorities%20have%20faced%20criticism%20from%20various%20quarters.%20Jharkhand%20BJP%20president%2C%20Babulal%20Marandi%2C%20expressed%20deep%20concern%2C%20alleging%20laxity%20within%20the%20law%20and%20order%20machinery%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20incident%20came%20up%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20Assembly%20during%20its%20concluding%20day%20of%20the%20budget%20session%2C%20leading%20to%20adjournments%20and%20heated%20debates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20finger-pointing%20gained%20momentum%20with%20the%20Opposition%20demanding%20the%20suspension%20of%20the%20Dumka%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20and%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20probe%20committee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709446560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Foot8t25k_police-generic_625x300_07_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthought-we-were-going-to-die-spanish-tourist-gang-raped-in-jharkhand-5167053%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20woman%2C%2028%2C%20was%20allegedly%20gang-raped%20by%20seven%20men%20when%20she%20was%20spending%20the%20night%20with%20her%20partner%20in%20a%20makeshift%20tent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F