)%2C%20%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20fifth%20day%2C%20he%20(Gandhi)%20will%20be%20in%20Ujjain%20and%20visit%20the%20holy%20Shri%20Mahakaleshwar%20temple%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20Lok%20Dal's%20participation%20in%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20recently%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%26quot%3B%20Lok%20Dal%20welcomed%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20during%20the%20yatra%20in%20Aligarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20posters%2C%20banners%20and%20hoardings%20of%20former%20PMs%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20the%20real%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20asli%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20RLD%20(Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal)%20is%20the%20nakli%20Lok%20Dal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RLD%20joined%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20after%20the%20central%20government%20recently%20conferred%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20posthumously%20on%20former%20PM%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20contest%20from%20the%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20(in%20Kerala)%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20under%20discussion%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20decide%20the%20seat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20BJP%20declaring%20its%20first%20list%20of%20195%20candidates%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-34-ministers-in-bjps-1st-list-of-195-candidates-for-lok-sabha-polls-5163186%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELok%20Sabha%20polls%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said%20why%20should%20he%20comment%20on%20the%20saffron%20party's%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20finalising%20our%20manifesto%2C%20our%20candidates%20and%20our%20seats%20in%20different%20states.%20My%20concern%20is%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20and%20not%20what%20the%20BJP%20is%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2F