3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bhopal%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20replaced%20Pragya%20Thakur%20with%20Alok%20Sharma.%20An%20accused%20in%20the%202008%20Malegaon%20bombings%20case%2C%20the%20firebrand%20leader's%20nomination%20last%20time%20had%20sparked%20a%20huge%20row.%20The%20five%20years%20since%20then%20have%20seen%20her%20getting%20caught%20in%20several%20controversies.%20Out%20on%20bail%20on%20health%20grounds%2C%20Ms%20Thakur%20has%20been%20seen%20playing%20kabaddi%20and%20attending%20garba%20nights.%20But%20the%20controversy%20that%20may%20have%20harmed%20her%20the%20most%20is%20a%20statement%20in%20which%20she%20called%20Nathuram%20Godse%2C%20the%20man%20who%20shot%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20dead%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bpatriot%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remark%20drew%20a%20stern%20response%20from%20none%20other%20than%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20%26quot%3BThe%20remarks%20made%20about%20Gandhiji%20or%20Nathuram%20Godse%20are%20very%20bad%20and%20very%20wrong%20for%20society.%20She%20has%20sought%20an%20apology%2C%20but%20I%20would%20never%20be%20able%20to%20forgive%20her%20fully%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Five%20years%20on%2C%20Ms%20Thakur%20has%20lost%20her%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Thakur%20was%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20another%20row%20for%20her%20remarks%20on%20former%20Mumbai%20ATS%20chief%20Hemant%20Karkare%2C%20who%20died%20during%20the%202008%20terror%20attacks.%20She%20had%20said%20he%20was%20killed%20because%20of%20her%20%26quot%3Bcurse%26quot%3B.%20Party%20sources%20said%20the%20firebrand%20leader%20was%20not%20active%20in%20her%20constituency%2C%20and%20that%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20her%20being%20dropped.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20omission%20in%20the%20BJP%20list%20that%20surprised%20many%20was%20West%20Delhi%20MP%20Parvesh%20Sahib%20Singh%20Verma.%20A%20two-time%20MP%20and%20son%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20late%20Sahib%20Singh%20Verma%2C%20he%20is%20known%20to%20have%20a%20strong%20support%20base.%20But%20the%2046-year-old%20leader%20has%20been%20in%20the%20news%20for%20his%20inciting%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%202020%20Delhi%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Verma%20had%20made%20controversial%20remarks%20during%20the%20Shaheen%20Bagh%20protest%20and%20said%20the%20demonstrators%20would%20be%20cleared%20in%20an%20hour%20if%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Mr%20Verma%20hit%20headlines%20again%2C%20this%20time%20for%20a%20public%20boycott%20call%20seemingly%20aimed%20at%20Muslims.%20%26quot%3BWherever%20you%20see%20them%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20fix%20their%20head%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20set%20them%20straight%2C%20then%20the%20only%20cure%20is%20total%20boycott.%20Raise%20your%20hand%20if%20you%20agree%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20MP%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20into%20the%202024%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20its%20goals%20clear.%20It%20wants%20to%20keep%20the%20focus%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20'Viksit%20Bharat%20%402047'%20call%20and%20does%20not%20want%20its%20leaders%20to%20make%20statements%20that%20serve%20as%20fodder%20for%20the%20Opposition%20and%20embarrass%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20MP%20who%20may%20have%20been%20axed%20for%20his%20remarks%20is%20South%20Delhi%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri.%20During%20a%20discussion%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20Mr%20Bidhuri%20used%20Islamophobic%20slurs%20for%20Amroha%20MP%20Danish%20Ali.%20The%20derogatory%20remarks%20were%20caught%20on%20camera%20and%20sparked%20a%20huge%20row.%20While%20the%20South%20Delhi%20MP%20later%20apologised%2C%20the%20BJP's%20first%20list%20shows%20it%20was%20not%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20prominent%20Delhi%20MPs%20who%20have%20been%20dropped%20include%20Meenakshi%20Lekhi%20and%20Harsh%20Vardhan.%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20had%20won%20every%20seat%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20in%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20faces%20a%20joint%20Opp