3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20has%20since%20also%20referred%20to%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassin%20Nathuram%20Godse%20as%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpragya-thakur-nathuram-godse-patriot-statement-bjp%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cpatriot%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20election%20trail%2C%20forcing%20the%20BJP%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20BJP%20vice%20president%20Alok%20Sharma%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Thakur%E2%80%99s%20Bhopal%20constituency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESouth%20Delhi%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20who%20used%20violent%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Framesh-bidhuri-parliament-privileges-panel%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eanti-Muslim%20slurs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20fellow%20parliamentarian%20Danish%20Ali%20during%20the%20monsoon%20session%20has%20also%20been%20dropped.%20The%20party%20has%20instead%20fielded%20Ramvir%20Singh%20Bidhuri%20from%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoS%20external%20affairs%20Meenakshi%20Lekhi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20New%20Delhi%20constituency%20has%20also%20been%20dropped%20and%20been%20instead%20been%20replaced%20by%20former%20external%20affairs%20minister%20Sushma%20Swaraj%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%20who%20serves%20as%20one%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20national%20spokespersons%20at%20present.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20East%20Delhi%20candidate%20has%20not%20been%20announced%2C%20sitting%20MP%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20announced%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20earlier%20on%20Saturday%20that%20he%20has%20communicated%20to%20party%20chief%20J.P.%20Nadda%20that%20will%20focus%20on%20his%20cricketing%20commitments%2C%20fuelling%20speculation%20that%20he%20may%20not%20be%20given%20a%20ticket.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20have%20requested%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Party%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJPNadda%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40JPNadda%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20to%20relieve%20me%20of%20my%20political%20duties%20so%20that%20I%20can%20focus%20on%20my%20upcoming%20cricket%20commitments.%20I%20sincerely%20thank%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20PM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20and%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20HM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShah%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AmitShah%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20for%20giving%20me%20the%20opportunity%20to%20serve%20the%20people.%20Jai%20Hind!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20(%40GautamGambhir)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGautamGambhir%2Fstatus%2F1763785102268772777%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20similar%20post%20was%20also%20put%20out%20by%20Jayant%20Sinha%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20MP%20from%20Hazaribagh.%20The%20list%20announced%20by%20the%20BJP%20just%20hours%20later%2C%20showed%20that%20Manish%20Jaiswal%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWho%E2%80%99s%20in%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20who%20helped%20the%20BJP%20win%20a%20record%20fifth%20term%20in%20the%20state%2C%20but%20was%20not%20made%20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20given%20the%20party%20ticket%20from%20Vidisha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoS%20home%20affairs%20Ajay%20%E2%80%98Teni%E2%80%99%20Mishra%20who%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Futtar-pradesh-ajay-mishra-teni-supreme-court%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esprung%20to%20the%20spotlight%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%202021%20after%20his%20son%20Ashish%20Mishra%20alias%20Monu%20and%20his%20associates%20were%20accused%20of%20murdering%20four%20farmers%20in%20Tikonia%20by%20mowing%20them%20down%20under%20their%20SUVs%20has%20been%20given%20a%20ticket%20again%20from%20Kheri.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20rewarded%20those%20who%20have%20switched%20over%20to%20the%20BJP%20from%20other%20opposition%20parties%20including%20Geeta%20Koda%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99%20lone%20MP%20from%20Jharkhand.%20Koda%20who%20joined%20the%20party%20earlier%20this%20week%20(February%2026)%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Singhbhum%20where%20she%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBB%20Patil%2C%20the%20MP%20from%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20Zahirabad%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20BJP%20from%20the%20BRS%20just%20yesterday%20(March%201)%20has%20also%20been%20fielded%20from%20the%20same%20seat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnil%20Antony%2C%20son%20of%20Congress%20veteran%20A.K.%20Antony%20who%20quit%20the%20Congress%20last%20April%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Pathanamthitta.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESaket%20Mishra%2C%20sitting%20MLC%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20assembly%20who%20is%20the%20son%20of%20former%20IAS%20officer%20Nripendra%20Misra%2C%20who%20served%20as%20principal%20secretary%20to%20Modi%20between%202014%20and%202019%20and%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20construction%20committee%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Shravasti.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20Tripura%20chief%20minister%20Biplab%20Kumar%20Deb%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Tripura%20West.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEatala%20Rajender%20who%20lost%20in%20the%202023%20Telangana%20assembly%20polls%20has%20also%20been%20given%20a%20ticket%20for%20t