3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20chapters%20drive%20home%20more%20home%20truths%20than%20others%2C%20thrusting%20the%20title%20of%20the%20book%20to%20greater%20prominence.%20As%20a%20reader%2C%20you%20nod%20when%20you%20learn%20of%20Pepys%20taking%20social%20distancing%20to%20mean%20distancing%20himself%20from%20the%20poor%20of%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAny%20reader%2C%20similarly%2C%20will%20be%20driven%20insane%20by%20the%20banality%20of%20how%20similar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcovid-19-tablighi-jamaat-hindu-muslim%5C%22%3Ereactions%20have%20been%20to%20minorities%20%E2%80%93%20often%20religious%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20across%20time%20and%20place%2C%20during%20disease%20outbreaks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20illustrate%20the%20universality%20of%20this%20wretchedness%2C%20Hauser%20uses%20words%20like%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcovid-19-corona-jihad-muslims-tablighi%5C%22%3Esuperspreaders%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20which%20were%20clearly%20not%20in%20vogue%20in%20Restoration%20England%2C%20but%20jolt%20something%20in%20the%20reader%20%E2%80%93%20urging%20her%20to%20admire%20the%20ridiculousness%20of%20the%20term%20in%20the%20age%20in%20which%20it%20belonged%20as%20well.%20It%20is%20somehow%20never%20the%20rich%20(and%20later%2C%20the%20dominant%20community%20members)%20who%20are%20superspreaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20so%20it%20is%20that%20in%20the%20prologue%2C%20Hauser%20presents%20the%20pithy%20heart%20of%20the%20book%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20did%20morality%20transform%20and%20what%20consequences%20did%20this%20have%20for%20social%20groups%20considered%20to%20have%20caused%20or%20increased%20the%20risk%20of%20contagion%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03093218%2Fthe-moral-contagion_4-1024x726.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03093218%2Fthe-moral-contagion_4-1024x726.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03093218%2Fthe-moral-contagion_4-300x213.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03093218%2Fthe-moral-contagion_4.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699832%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22596%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20illustration%20from%20%E2%80%98The%20Moral%20Contagion%E2%80%99%20by%20Julia%20Hauser%20and%20Sarnath%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%20also%20presents%20the%20history%20of%20science%20with%20a%20firm%20eye%20on%20the%20role%20of%20colonial%20practices%20%E2%80%93%20placing%20laconic%20credit%20for%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20disease%20to%20the%20British%20and%20their%20commerce%20wherever%20due.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBanerjee%E2%80%99s%20art%20is%20the%20jester%20traipsing%20through%20the%20expanse%20of%20the%20book.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20pages%20have%20illustrations%20%E2%80%93%20so%20the%20total%20number%20of%20drawings%20is%20close%20to%20130.%20The%20text%20%E2%80%93%20never%20dry%20but%20certainly%20more%20serious%20than%20the%20art%20%E2%80%93%20scooches%20to%20a%20corner%20to%20make%20way%20for%20it.%20Banerjee%20harnesses%20his%20telltale%20style%20%E2%80%93%20crayon%20marks%20visible%2C%20faces%20dour%20and%20experiences%20muted%20on%20one%20page%20and%20viscerally%20exaggerated%20on%20the%20next.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20sick%20man%20in%20Bombay%20stretches%20comically%20as%20two%20policemen%20drag%20him%20away%20by%20the%20legs%2C%20almost%20bored.%20Things%20happen%20to%20people%20he%20draws%2C%20but%20not%20acutely%20enough%20to%20rob%20his%20characters%20of%20humour.%20It%20is%20minimal%2C%20so%20whenever%20it%20is%20opulent%2C%20the%20details%20take%20you%20by%20surprise.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPages%2082%20and%2083%20are%20something%20of%20a%20triumph.%20Here%2C%20a%20body%20is%20seen%20lurching%20into%20the%20sea%20from%20a%20ship%20instituted%20as%20a%20plague%20hospital%20off%20Hong%20Kong%20by%20the%20British.%20The%20night%20is%20dark%20and%20the%20enormity%20of%20the%20ship%20is%20perhaps%20a%20testament%20to%20how%20stuffy%2C%20how%20claustrophobic%20such%20an%20exercise%20must%20have%20felt%20to%20Chinese%20colonial%20subjects%20suffering%20from%20an%20exhausting%20disease.%20The%20drawing%20occupies%20almost%20one-and-a-half%20pages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20ubiquitousness%20of%20injustice%2C%20some%20details%20are%20particularly%20sobering.%20Like%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20plague%20came%20back%20to%20Hong%20Kong%20every%20year%20for%20three%20decades%20in%20the%20late%2019th%20and%20early%2020th%20centuries%2C%20and%20yet%20there%20was%20no%20interest%20in%20investing%20in%20the%20health%20of%20the%20workers%20who%20ran%20it.%20While%20those%20suffering%20from%20long%20COVID%20continue%20to%20remind%20us%20of%20the%20crushing%20after-effects%20of%20it%2C%20while%20those%20who%20lost%20loved%20ones%20in%20disease%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcoronavirus-national-lockdown-migrant-workers-dead%5C%22%3Ealso%20thanks%20to%20harebrained%20policy%20decisions%20surrounding%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20unlikely%20to%20ever%20forget%20it%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20exaggeration%20to%20say%20that%20the%20pandemic%20lies%20forgotten%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20Conclusion%2C%20Hauser%20says%20that%20even%20this%20is%20common.%20Even%20more%20chastening%2C%20often%20it%20is%20%E2%80%98bigger%E2%80%99%2