%20conveys%20the%20legacy%20of%20Rajasthani%20culture.%20The%20sensation%20of%20tactility%20is%20achieved%20through%20the%20Royale%20Play%20range%20of%20textured%20paints%20from%20Asian%20Paints%2C%20which%20turns%20simple%20surfaces%20into%20tactile%20language%20that%20the%20students%20can%20touch%20and%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20textured%20paints%20add%20a%20new%20dimension%20and%20redefine%20the%20art%2C%20says%20Amit%20Syngle%2C%20MD%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%2C%20Asian%20Paints%20Ltd.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20Asian%20Paints%2C%20we%20leverage%20art%20and%20creativity%20to%20foster%20inclusivity%20among%20people.%20Sparsh%20is%20a%20representation%20of%20our%20values%20of%20empathy%20and%20the%20spirit%20of%20creativity.%20This%20initiative%20aims%20to%20bring%20joy%20and%20inspiration%20to%20visually%20impaired%20students%20through%20touch%20and%20feel.%20The%20murals%20narrate%20captivating%20stories%2C%20from%20the%20rich%20heritage%20of%20Rajasthan%20to%20the%20indomitable%20spirit%20of%20Helen%20Keller%20and%20are%20accessible%20to%20all%2C%20especially%20people%20who%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318714%2Ftamil-nadu-engineer-turns-artist-paints-with-sunlight-vignesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperceive%20the%20world%20differently%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20us.%20Together%20with%20St%2Bart%20India%20Foundation%2C%20the%20Sparsh%20initiative%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20commitment%20to%20%23ArtForAll.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Finclusivity-in-art-6-1709208239.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20space%20is%20divided%20into%20an%20outdoor%20art%20mural%2C%20an%20indoor%20art%20museum%20and%20an%20art%20workshop%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-