e%20US%20cost%20a%20million%20dollars.%20Our%20solution%20is%20the%20most%20affordable%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20will%20also%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20weeding%20cycles%20and%20time.%20Such%20technology%20is%20not%20available%20in%20India%20and%20we%20have%20also%20applied%20for%20a%20patent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20other%20available%20machines%20use%20carbon%20dioxide-based%20technology%2C%20are%20huge%2C%20and%20have%20a%20high%20maintenance%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20solutions%20use%20invisible%20laser%20technology%20while%20we%20use%20blue%20laser%20light%20which%20penetrates%20faster%20through%20chlorophyll%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20and%20his%20team%20built%20the%20implement%20over%20eight%20months%20and%20have%20conducted%20trials%20in%20farms%20across%20India.%20Harvested%20Robotics%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Microsoft%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343156%2Ftoxin-free-home-cleaning-products-delhi-simran-khara-koparo-startup-shark-tank-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStartups%20Founders%20Hub%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they%20are%20also%20working%20with%20Mahindra%20%26amp%3B%20Mahindra%20to%20test%20their%20product.%20They%20are%20gearing%20up%20to%20launch%20their%20product%20in%20the%20market%20in%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20and%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20priced%20at%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20more%20information%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20Rahul%20at%20rahul%40harvestedlabs.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709043839000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frahul-arepaka-1709043428.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343321%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Founder%20of%20Harvested%20Robotics%2C%20Rahul%2