an%20admit%20their%20paraplegic%20dogs.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20from%20Kerala%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Hyderabad%20and%20even%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20call%20us%20to%20ask%20whether%20they%20can%20admit%20paraplegic%20dogs%20into%20our%20shelter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSarah-Iyer-Dog-Shelter-Image-45-1708958966.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sarah%20with%20her%20dogs.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSarah-Iyer-Dog-Shelter-Image-45-1708958966.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSarah-Iyer-Dog-Shelter-Image-45-1708958966-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSarah-Iyer-Dog-Shelter-Image-45-1708958966-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSarah-Iyer-Dog-Shelter-Image-45-1708958966-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSarah-Iyer-Dog-Shelter-Image-45-1708958966-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343239%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESarah%20playing%20with%20the%20dogs%20in%20her%20shelter.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDealing%20with%20loss%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20dream%20is%20to%20have%20no%20dogs%20suffer%20on%20the%20streets.%20Backed%20by%20an%20extremely%20robust%20animal%20birth%20control%20program%20and%20proper%20shelters%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20see%20fewer%20dogs%20on%20the%20streets.%20With%20their%20numbers%20on%20the%20street%20reduced%2C%20there%20will%20be%20fewer%20accidents%20and%20fewer%20paraplegic%20dogs%20as%20well.%20We%20wish%20to%20showcase%20this%20here%20in%20Chennai%20and%20then%20roll%20it%20out%20through%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20work%20required%20in%20caring%20for%20them%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20an%20emotionally%20draining%20process.%20Some%20of%20these%20dogs%20come%20into%20this%20shelter%20as%20puppies%20and%20she%20cares%20for%20them%20all%20their%20life.%20Eventually%2C%20however%2C%20they%20pass%20away.%20How%20does%20she%20deal%20with%20that%20emotional%20toll%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHonestly%2C%20whenever%20one%20of%20my%20dogs%20passes%20away%2C%20I%20tell%20Gerry%20that%20I%20want%20to%20shut%20the%20shelter%20down.%20Recently%2C%20I%20lost%20a%20German%20Shepherd%20called%20Zain.%20He%20was%20my%20dearest%20baby.%20He%20came%20to%20us%20as%20a%20three-month-old%20pup%20with%20his%20pelvis%20crushed%20and%20by%20the%20time%20he%20was%20ten%20months%20old%2C%20he%20had%20become%20this%20massive%20fellow%20following%20me%20around%20everywhere.%20We%20name%20all%20the%20dogs%20in%20our%20shelter%20and%20choose%20them%20according%20to%20their%20personality.%20I%E2%80%99m%20still%20grieving%20for%20that%20boy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20an%20old%20dog%20stays%20with%20us%20for%20two%20months%20and%20passes%20away%2C%20it%20tears%20me%20up%20from%20within.%20I%E2%80%99m%20shattered%20for%20the%20next%20few%20days%20until%20I%20see%20a%20video%20of%20another%20dog%20or%20puppy%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Chennai%20who%20needs%20our%20assistance.%20I%20focus%20my%20energy%20on%20helping%20that%20dog.%20I%20find%20a%20way%20to%20block%20that%20pain%20by%20immersing%20myself%20in%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20other%20dogs%20in%20our%20care.%20But%20it%20also%20gives%20me%20great%20joy%20seeing%20these%20dogs%20get%20shelter%2C%20recover%2C%20and%20play%20around%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3ESarah%20needs%20your%20assistance%20to%20ma